                    />

            
    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">Oil wells cover the landscape near Loco Hills, New Mexico, which sits in the Permian Basin, a major oil- and gas-producing area in West Texas and southeastern New Mexico.</span>
    
